{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398560/extras/run_a_shop_quicker_final.gif?t=1739575441\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398560/extras/defend.gif?t=1739575441\" /><br>Mario Meatballs has always yearned to create the ultimate pizzeria, and now that he's found a spot within his budget, his dream has become a reality. But there's a reason why the real estate was such a steal...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this thrilling pizza-making simulation with a dash of tower defense, you'll step into Mario's shoes and manage every aspect of running a brick-and-mortar shop by day then at night fend off hordes of crazed lunatics and other totally normal things for a small business owner.\u00a0\u00a0<br><br><u>Key Features</u><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398560/extras/map.gif?t=1739575441\" /><u></u> <br>\u25a0\u00a0<strong>Multi-Leveled Puzzles and Challenges</strong>: Engaging gameplay loops that include cooking simulations, tower defense strategies, competitive multiplayer modes, and team-based challenges.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398560/extras/teams.gif?t=1739575441\" /><br> <br>\u25a0\u00a0<strong>Multiplayer Co-op</strong>: Challenge your friendships by playing against them or play on the same side and upgrade your shop to the best of your crews abilities<br><br> <br>\u25a0\u00a0<strong>OST</strong>: Original Soundtrack and sound effects crafted by Brightside Movement, enhancing the culinary adventure. <br>\u25a0\u00a0<strong>Immersive Graphics</strong>: A unique stylized environment that helps create a vibrant and delicious world where players can truly experience the art of pizza making and tomatoe sauce spilling\u00a0</p>","background":"https://sh